OL,3,CProtest over electricity price hike
OL,4,Cthat 'will ruin lives'
OL,6,FMore than 1,300 people have signed a
OL,7,Fpetition calling for the States to
OL,8,Fblock Guernsey Electricity from
OL,9,Fintroducing its planned 8% price hike
OL,10,Fon 1 July.
OL,12,FAround one hundred customers also took
OL,13,Fto the streets at the weekend to voice
OL,14,Ftheir concerns outside the utility
OL,15,Fcompany's headquarters in St Sampson.
OL,17,FThe petition's creator and protest
OL,18,Forganiser Myles Duquemin says Guernsey
OL,19,Fis "turning into a playground for the
OL,20,Frich" and "greed is slowly but surely
OL,21,Fpushing everyday people out".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
