OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1750328941
OL,3,CProtest over electricity price hike
OL,4,Cthat 'will ruin lives'
OL,6,FHe argues that Guernsey Electricity's
OL,7,Fdecision to raise tariffs above the
OL,8,Frate of inflation, which stands at
OL,9,F4.2%, will "ruin lives" and puts extra
OL,10,Fpressure on "many full-time workers
OL,11,Fwho are already on the brink of
OL,12,Fhomelessness".
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, he adds: "When
OL,15,Fyou've put it above inflation year
OL,16,Fafter year, how are you expecting the
OL,17,Fpublic to pay for that?
OL,19,F"I think it's unrealistic to think
OL,20,Fthat's going to be the way it is for
OL,21,Fthe rest of time."
