OL,3,CProtest over electricity price hike
OL,4,Cthat 'will ruin lives'
OL,6,F"The company has worked hard to keep
OL,7,Fthis year's electricity tariff
OL,8,Fincrease as low as possible, balancing
OL,9,Fthis with the need to invest the
OL,10,Fappropriate amount in our electricity
OL,11,Finfrastructure to maintain a secure
OL,12,Fsupply to our customers with minimal
OL,13,Finterruptions, against a backdrop
OL,14,Fwhere the company was unable to raise
OL,15,Ftariffs for a decade.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
