OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1750328941
OL,3,CProtest over electricity price hike
OL,4,Cthat 'will ruin lives'
OL,6,F"To minimise the burden on customers
OL,7,Fas much as possible, we have, again,
OL,8,Fsought to achieve an appropriate
OL,9,Fbalance to fund this essential
OL,10,Finvestment through a mix of additional
OL,11,Fdebt financing and tariff increases.
OL,13,F"However, this additional debt and
OL,14,Fcontinued high interest rates means
OL,15,Fthat we also face increased borrowing
OL,16,Fcosts."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
