OL,4,Cthat 'will ruin lives'
OL,6,FMr Bates says that Guernsey
OL,7,FElectricity is in #50 million of debt
OL,8,Fand introducing the price hike now
OL,9,Fwill protect customers from larger
OL,10,Fincreases going forward.
OL,12,FAround 90% of Guernsey's power comes
OL,13,Fthrough a cable from France via
OL,14,FJersey, but that deal with French
OL,15,Fenergy company EDF runs out in 2027.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
