OL,6,FHe adds: "The historical supply
OL,7,Fcontracts which have shielded the
OL,8,Fisland from the large increases seen
OL,9,Fin the UK and Europe post Ukraine are
OL,10,Fcoming to a close, so prices
OL,11,Funfortunately will inevitably need to
OL,12,Frise from this base to more accurately
OL,13,Freflect prevailing wholesale market
OL,14,Fprices which remain higher than pre
OL,15,Fthe Ukraine conflict."
